            <description>The "Bennu pseudo-ranging" data product consists of a table giving DSN range measurements of the OSIRIS-REx spacecraft as if the measurements were received and transmitted by Bennu. This product was produced by the OSIRIS-REx science team and 
was used to estimate the ephemeris of Bennu, Yarkovsky effect, and YORP effect.</description>
